  "text": "The finding, however, of constitutive Wnt/β-catenin signaling in the entire peritumoral adrenal cortex, [CITATION_1] in micro-and macronodular hyperplasia, and in nonaldosterone-producing adrenocortical tumors challenges this contention. [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Thus, whether SFRP2 and Wnt/β-catenin can isolate aldosteroneproducing cells and identify APA is doubtful.",
